text:
Name: Mary Hernandez.
Graduation Year: 2022.
Description: Mary Hernandez is a dedicated Anthropology student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in anthropology research and practical applications. They aspire to become a mechanical engineer working on cutting-edge robotics and automation. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
